817
00:49:50,650 --> 00:49:52,549
Now, unless you want
to get into a contest,

818
00:49:52,550 --> 00:49:55,193
drop the gun and get out of here.

819
00:49:59,490 --> 00:50:01,007
I said drop the gun!

820
00:50:01,008 --> 00:50:01,841
- Okay.

821
00:50:01,841 --> 00:50:02,841
All right.

822
00:50:05,100 --> 00:50:06,113
- I told you.

823
00:50:07,284 --> 00:50:09,017
- [Crystal] The cops are on their way.

824
00:50:10,210 --> 00:50:11,659
- Come on! Let's go!

825
00:50:11,660 --> 00:50:12,660
- No!

826
00:50:13,560 --> 00:50:14,649
It's over.

827
00:50:14,650 --> 00:50:17,299
This whole cockamamie charade is over.

828
00:50:17,300 --> 00:50:18,649
Finished.

829
00:50:18,650 --> 00:50:19,650
- Really?

830
00:50:20,800 --> 00:50:22,790
All right, come on, come on.

831
00:50:22,791 --> 00:50:23,817
- Go ahead.

832
00:50:23,818 --> 00:50:24,701
Do it.

833
00:50:24,701 --> 00:50:25,534
Do it.

834
00:50:25,534 --> 00:50:26,460
- Cut it out.

835
00:50:26,461 --> 00:50:28,189
- What's the matter? No guts?

836
00:50:28,190 --> 00:50:29,190
- Cam, don't.

837
00:50:30,422 --> 00:50:31,260
- I'm trying.

838
00:50:31,261 --> 00:50:32,529
- Come on.

839
00:50:32,530 --> 00:50:35,149
What do you think I bought this gun for?

840
00:50:35,150 --> 00:50:37,549
Come on, take your best shot.

841
00:50:37,550 --> 00:50:38,550
Punk!

842
00:50:40,040 --> 00:50:41,040
- No.

843
00:50:43,430 --> 00:50:45,544
Do something!

844
00:50:45,545 --> 00:50:48,108
(hits)
(Gordon grunts)

845
00:50:48,109 --> 00:50:50,692
(Gordon thuds)

846
00:50:53,269 --> 00:50:56,668
♪ Papa I think I messed up again ♪

847
00:50:56,669 --> 00:50:58,348
♪ Was it something I did ♪

848
00:50:58,349 --> 00:51:00,643
♪ Was it something I said ♪

849
00:51:00,644 --> 00:51:02,293
