- Hey!

850
00:51:02,294 --> 00:51:03,294
Cut it out!

851
00:51:03,295 --> 00:51:05,586
- You're driving too fast.

852
00:51:05,587 --> 00:51:06,500
And you, I'm not gonna say it again.

