- You're hurting me.

855
00:51:09,310 --> 00:51:10,959
- You touch her again, I swear to God-

856
00:51:10,960 --> 00:51:11,960
- What?

857
00:51:13,207 --> 00:51:14,975
- No you don't have it.

858
00:51:14,976 --> 00:51:16,059
No you don't.

859
00:51:17,009 --> 00:51:19,111
(slaps)
(Cam grunts)

860
00:51:19,112 --> 00:51:20,051
- Are you deaf?

861
00:51:20,052 --> 00:51:21,377
- Ow!

862
00:51:21,378 --> 00:51:22,805
- I said slow down.

863
00:51:22,806 --> 00:51:24,056
- [Crystal] Ow!

864
00:51:26,451 --> 00:51:31,451
♪ That it's time to get
down on my knees and pray ♪

865
00:51:33,242 --> 00:51:34,932
♪ Lord undo me ♪
- No, come on.

866
00:51:34,933 --> 00:51:36,026
Get out of the car.

867
00:51:36,027 --> 00:51:37,410
Get out of the car!

868
00:51:39,295 --> 00:51:41,694
You wanna kill yourself,
you go right ahead.

869
00:51:41,695 --> 00:51:44,088
♪ This spirit through me ♪

870
00:51:44,089 --> 00:51:44,922
♪ Lord ♪

871
00:51:44,923 --> 00:51:47,488
- [Jodi] You need to eat.

872
00:51:47,489 --> 00:51:49,656
♪ Undo me ♪

873
00:52:03,853 --> 00:52:07,074
♪ But I never meant to hurt you ♪

874
00:52:07,075 --> 00:52:09,075
I'm not feeling so good.

875
00:52:10,644 --> 00:52:12,567
What if he really does it?

876
00:52:12,568 --> 00:52:14,135
- [Crystal] Don't talk about it.

877
00:52:14,136 --> 00:52:14,969
- Yeah.

878
00:52:14,970 --> 00:52:18,990
We saved that guy and his
bunions too many times.

879
00:52:20,077 --> 00:52:22,327
It's what he wanted anyway.

880
00:52:23,348 --> 00:52:26,487
♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

881
00:52:26,488 --> 00:52:28,484
- Maybe we should go back.

882
00:52:28,485 --> 00:52:30,302
- Are you nuts?

883
00:52:30,303 --> 00:52:31,303
No way.

884
00:52:35,320 --> 00:52:37,903
(wind blowing)

885
00:53:04,696 --> 00:53:06,946
(laughing)

886
00:53:24,238 --> 00:53:26,655
